com.appboy

Interface IAppboyUnitySupport

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Appboy

    public interface IAppboyUnitySupport
    IAppboyUnitySupport exists to provide functionality uniquely required to enable communication between the Appboy SDK and Unity projects. Though these functions can be called from client code if necessary, by default they should only be accessed by Appboy code. Any other use case is advanced and should only be done if a clear and definite need arises.
